    <title>Hexo Pro后台管理界面</title>
    <url>/2024/08/15/Hexo-Pro%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%B0%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1>安装Hexo pro</h1>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-pro</span><br><span class="line">hexo server -d</span><br><span class="line">open http://localhost:4000/pro/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1>配置登陆账户与密码</h1>
<p>需要在hexo的_config.yml中增加以下配置来使用账户密码登陆后台，不配置后台会直接登陆。 配置后使用jwt来保护后台访问的接口</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo_pro:</span><br><span class="line">  username: admim</span><br><span class="line">  password: 123</span><br><span class="line">  avatar: https: image for your own avata</span><br><span class="line">  secret: xxx // jwt secret key</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
